lyrics:
[verse]
In the darkened depths, a raging flame ignites
Egor Letov's death, mourned by the sleepless nights
Chaotic whispers calling from the other side
A symphony of shadows, where death does not abide

[chorus]
Aggressive screams, echo through the night
The spirit of Letov, still shines bright
Blackened embers, burning in our hearts
As we unite, in this psychedelic art
style: psychedelic, experimental, very fast, growling, Black metal
